data.description: This distinctive property, nestled in the renowned Lower Moreland School District, is a true gem. Bathed in natural light, the home boasts a bright and airy ambiance with numerous updates both inside and out. Throughout, you'll find stunning hardwood floors that add a touch of elegance. The kitchen, renovated in 2016, is a highlight with stainless steel appliances and exquisite granite countertops.  The open floor plan flows seamlessly, leading to a spacious patio through walk-out sliding doors. The bathrooms feature beautiful tiles, complemented by newer vanities and medicine cabinets. Upstairs, three generously sized bedrooms are enhanced by professionally crafted custom closets, offering ample space and abundant natural light. The finished basement provides extra living space, complete with additional storage and a utility area.  Recently painted, the property also features a unique transformation: the two-car garage has been converted into a well-equipped workshop/office area with heating and air conditioning; however could easily be converted back to a 2-car garage! This property has plenty of parking spots, with a long driveway and easy, neighborhood-access to drive right through into the driveway.  Schedule your appointment TODAY and visit us at our OPEN HOUSE on Saturday, 10/14/23 from 11am-2pm and Sunday 10/15/23 11am-1pm
